<module>
    <h>thu</h>
    <p><g>thu</g>
        <en>you, thou</en> is the second person singular <a href="?xx=nouns/personal_pronouns"
            >personal pronoun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <section id="verbs-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <!--<p><g>thu</g> can be used as the subject of a verb.</p>-->
            <p>Examples with the predicative verb <g href="?gd=bi">bi</g>
                <en>be</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha thu trang.</gd>
                        <tr>You are busy.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil thu ag obair? Chan eil.</gd>
                        <tr>Are you working? No, I’m not.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9 [226] [adapted]</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An robh thu sgìth? Bha.</gd>
                        <tr>Were you tired? Yes, I was.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 16</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil thu a’ fuireach? Tha mi a’ fuireach anns a’ chlachan.</gd>
                        <tr>Where do you live? I live in the village.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Nach do dh’<a href="?gd=ool">òl</a> thu do thì? Cha do dh’òl. Cha do chuir thu siùcar
                            ann.</gd>
                        <tr>Didn’t you drink your tea? No, I didn’t. You didn’t put sugar in
                            it.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 48</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do <a href="?gd=buail">bhuail</a> thu an cù? Bhuail.</gd>
                        <tr>Did you strike the dog? Yes, I did.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>





